{"tid":1162240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同群姐演一對，歐陽震華客串兩集《愛‧回家》","createTime":"2019-05-19T17:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:17:45.000Z","uid":23451,"like":387,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"24d3b206831d6f06671b1480a1b32b9a25bad66b","tid":1162240,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/20/spKTvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F20%2FspKTvR.png&h=aade1d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向來是大台收視福將的歐陽震華（Bobby），昨晚他現身電視城，穿上古裝化身當年他在經典劇集《金裝四大才子》中演過的「祝枝山」一角，今次他為處境劇《愛‧回家之開心速遞》客串，還與在劇中飾演清潔阿姐的群姐（許思敏）演一對。<br />\n昨晚歐陽震華透露他在劇中會以「祝枝山」登場，而拍檔群姐則飾演花魁。今次Bobby客串原來是他自薦的，他表示有次找曾勵珍（珍姐），談及想在《愛》劇中客串，珍姐還以為他說笑，之後便安排了今次客串兩集的戲份。由於群姐曾表示好喜歡Bobby，今次與對方合作，如夢想成真，她表現得十分興奮，還讓Bobby托住她的香腮合照。至於收視方面，Bobby希望能衝破30點，如收視理想，檔期和劇組許可的話，Bobby不介意再來客串。此外，Bobby透露將於年底與萬綺雯合作拍一部警匪劇，他將會飾演警察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前歐陽波比拍過條片讚群姐<br />\n估唔到講真真係去自薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7thZ3rZAIk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7thZ3rZAIk4&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1z632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=8b0ff61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7thZ3rZAIk4</a>"},{"pid":"412e9b82a17117f98e3b600e79e5a937bef5b2fc","tid":1162240,"uid":23451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7447f699912a70e86f6e57ffed1003983ebe88f","tid":1162240,"uid":253623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0